,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"香港在理論上享有中國其他地方公民所不享有的某些自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b45ae9a4165f77d7345a6a4a248f7ceee22d87","tid":1603224,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:54:30.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"76fd06421e50dc4a950b18a164bc0adffc0e28f3","tid":1603224,"uid":181257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"903606f6ceccf93d993393737bacb5101f109077","tid":1603224,"uid":67816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:52:07.000Z","msg":"香港在理論上享有中國其他地方公民所不享有的某些自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"國際已知嘅事實"},{"pid":"27a821f3a45bb9bcd5db66fd3679f7bb9b11c6d6","tid":1603224,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5930dee6e3e1f06e3723dcf4338bcb805e30e41d","tid":1603224,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:58:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc92d6a0f65f473744fb3b7fb8bec9829e0492a3","tid":1603224,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"[twitter懶人包]全部同我入泥！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602587</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13a0f4d3072026b396147704f8c991ec1e5c918d","tid":1603224,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:00:56.000Z","msg":"比佢地睇下 佢地以前既澳門變成點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[cls警世系列] 澳門大三巴搞成咁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603125</a>"},{"pid":"375383d3ed5d2a90750c205cceeafe3adb73b7b3","tid":1603224,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"國際戰線好重要"},{"pid":"a9eb66c1bb8d90546e281b58a3a3973aa2e1846d","tid":1603224,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"國際戰線好重要"},{"pid":"239490e4645c3b6e8b6e3fa0d865ce58c0efc89b","tid":1603224,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T05:01:37.000Z","msg":"呢個需要澳門巴打幫手<br />\n澳門巴打，如果你係葡國公民，麻煩趁此機會去信葡國國會，要求葡國國會就中國違反《中葡聯合聲明》採取行動"}]}